title: Alcohol 120% -  tried and true, no viruses, no bullshit - Biggy
description:
The other day when I was at school I needed to install a program via a .iso and I didn't have alcohol on my laptop yet. I went to try and find a version to download quick and I couldn't find anything but shit. Either it was loaded with spyware or the shitty keygens it was packaged with didn't actually work. I came to realize there was a serious issue with trying to find alcohol 120% anywhere. So here is my clean 100% guaranteed to work version that I've been using for a long time. It's not the absolute latest but it has almost everything save blue-ray support/format. Works great for making images of CDs, burning images of several different formats (.iso, .mds, .bwt, .b5t, .b6t, .ccd, .cue, .bin, etc...), and use virtual drives to emulate disks.


Operating systems: MS Windows 2000/XP/Vista 32bit/64bit
Note: doesn't work on windows 7 build 6933
Homepage: http://www.alcohol-software.com


The installer is really nice and pretty straight forward. It was a program written by a third party that has the serial and installer in one.

If you have any issues please leave a comment.



-Biggy
